18#ifndef _LVM_FS_H
19#define _LVM_FS_H
20
21#include "metadata.h"
22
23/*
24 * These calls, private to the activate unit, set
25 * up the volume group directory in /dev and the
26 * symbolic links to the dm device.
27 */
28int fs_add_lv(const struct logical_volume *lv, const char *dev);
29int fs_del_lv(const struct logical_volume *lv);
30int fs_del_lv_byname(const char *dev_dir, const char *vg_name, const char *lv_name);
31int fs_rename_lv(struct logical_volume *lv, const char *dev,
32 const char *old_vgname, const char *old_lvname);
33void fs_unlock(void);
34
35#endif
